highlights.text: “Ponni Nadhi (From "Ponniyin Selvan Part -1") - Tamil” by A.R. Rahman, A. R. Reihana, and Bamba Bakya is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Bengaluru, up 37 spots at #12.
“Singara Siriye” by B. Ajaneesh Loknath, Vijay Prakash, Ananya Bhat, and Nagraj Panar Valtur is the highest new entry on Top Songs Bengaluru at #21.
Anirudh Ravichander has the most spots on Top Songs Bengaluru. “Megham Karukatha” is the highest at #5.
“Raataan Lambiyan (From "Shershaah")” by Tanishk Bagchi, Jubin Nautiyal, and Asees Kaur has been on Top Songs Bengaluru the longest, at 51 weeks straight.
